  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/06b35613b59e46ff5aa315811c198a21.avif?t=1662893347\" width=610 height=210 /></span><br><br>In the game you have to jump, push off walls and Electra accelerators. The protagonist JAD is a distant relative of AVA.<br><br>JAD is the most advanced and agile inhabitant of the planet Koitii.<br><br>Game features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dangerous saws<br></li><li>Jumping from walls and boosters<br></li><li>Jigsaw puzzles<br></li><li>Convenient management<br></li><li>Difficult levels</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/0a319900637baf98f87305911fd01c43.poster.avif?t=1662893347\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/0a319900637baf98f87305911fd01c43.webm?t=1662893347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/0a319900637baf98f87305911fd01c43.mp4?t=1662893347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/460ffd4893ec504df6592d2e07632d0a.poster.avif?t=1662893347\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/460ffd4893ec504df6592d2e07632d0a.webm?t=1662893347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/460ffd4893ec504df6592d2e07632d0a.mp4?t=1662893347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/06b35613b59e46ff5aa315811c198a21.avif?t=1662893347\" width=610 height=210 /></span><br><br>In the game you have to jump, push off walls and Electra accelerators. The protagonist JAD is a distant relative of AVA.<br><br>JAD is the most advanced and agile inhabitant of the planet Koitii.<br><br>Game features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dangerous saws<br></li><li>Jumping from walls and boosters<br></li><li>Jigsaw puzzles<br></li><li>Convenient management<br></li><li>Difficult levels</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/0a319900637baf98f87305911fd01c43.poster.avif?t=1662893347\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/0a319900637baf98f87305911fd01c43.webm?t=1662893347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/0a319900637baf98f87305911fd01c43.mp4?t=1662893347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/460ffd4893ec504df6592d2e07632d0a.poster.avif?t=1662893347\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/460ffd4893ec504df6592d2e07632d0a.webm?t=1662893347\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1447060/extras/460ffd4893ec504df6592d2e07632d0a.mp4?t=1662893347\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
